cu.explanation_en: Setting the second ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the second ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.
du.explanation_zh: 將第二個加密算法設定為未知的枚舉值 'nea9'，會在安全協商階段導致協商失敗，並造成 NAS 註冊被拒絕。
